    "## Step 4 — Model Architecture and Training Setup\n",
    "\n",
    "Define the EfficientNet-B0 based classifier with a custom head tailored to the number of target character classes.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Architecture summary:**\n",
    "- **Backbone:** EfficientNet-B0 (ImageNet pre-trained, fully unfrozen for fine-tuning)\n",
    "- **Head:** Dropout (p=0.3) → Linear(1280, num_classes)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Loss function:** Weighted Focal Loss with γ=2.0 to address class imbalance and focus training on hard examples.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Training configuration:**\n",
    "\n",
    "| Hyperparameter | Value |\n",
    "| :--- | :--- |\n",
    "| Optimiser | AdamW |\n",
    "| Learning rate | 1×10⁻⁴ |\n",
    "| Scheduler | CosineAnnealingLR (η_min = 1×10⁻⁶) |\n",
    "| Epochs | 80 (early-stop at high training accuracy) |\n",
    "| Batch size | 16 |"
   ]
  },
