   "source": [
    "## Step 6 — Inference on Test Set\n",
    "\n",
    "Load the fine-tuned YOLO detector and the trained EfficientNet classifier. For each test image:\n",
    "1. YOLO detects candidate character bounding boxes from `intermediate_boxes_expanded.json`.\n",
    "2. Each crop is resized to 224×224, normalised with ImageNet statistics, and classified.\n",
    "3. The predicted Unicode label and bounding box are recorded.\n",
    "\n",
    "> **Model paths:** Ensure `YOLO_MODEL_PATH` and `CLASSIFIER_MODEL_PATH` point to the correct `.pt` / `.pth` files for your environment."
   ]
